						<p><hi rend="bold">Rājādhirāja I. Year 12: A.D. 1030.</hi></p>						

						<p>The inscription records that the stone temple <hi rend="italic">(kaṟṟaḷi)</hi> was built for Sivapādasēkhara Mūvēndavēḷāṉ of the village Kuṇukkarumpu by Mārkkaṇḍaiyan <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kūḻappiḍāraṉ, a <hi rend="italic">sthapati</hi> from Tiruvālaṅgāḍu.</p>						

